meeting-recorder-core
======================

This project is a derivative work of Hyprnote ("char") by Fastrepl Inc.
Upstream: https://github.com/fastrepl/char
License:  GPL-3.0-or-later (same as upstream)

We include portions of the Hyprnote workspace — primarily the audio
capture, resampling, chunking, speech-to-text streaming, and listener
plumbing crates — and adapt them into a standalone library intended to
be consumed as a Cargo path / git dependency by downstream desktop apps.

Per GPL-3, any binary linking against this crate must itself be
licensed under GPL-3-compatible terms. Quantum's web app (Next.js,
private repository) does not link against any code in this repo and is
therefore not affected.

See LICENSE for the full text of the GNU General Public License v3.

Third-party runtime dependency:
  Cactus (cactus-sys) — https://github.com/cactus-compute/cactus
  Used for on-device streaming speech-to-text on Apple Silicon. License
  terms are set by Cactus Compute and are independent from this project.
